{
  "stem": "27390.4",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So he gave an order, you mustn't cut into a loaf.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "You've got to give the whole loaf, to each person, for the week, for seven days, a loaf, which was a very good idea.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Because you couldn't pinch anything.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "The people that distributed bread couldn't pinch.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But if a person got a loaf of bread, for a whole week, and he was starving, not everybody could hold himself back and keep the bread for the seven days.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So they finished a loaf in-- in two or three days.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And the rest of the week, they were starving.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I managed to control myself.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "My younger brother, he-- he couldn't.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He-- his bread-- his ration, he was finished with it after a few days.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So my mother had to give it, from her ration, to subsidize his ration, he should.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Because he had-- otherwise, he would have starved, completely.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Anyway, the-- the starvation rate went up, very high, in-- in 1940.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And there was literally hundreds of people dying, every day, from hunger.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And then other trouble started.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Diarrhea, dysentery, typhoid started.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And there were no medicines coming in.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "There were doctors, but they couldn't do anything.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "They had no medicines.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So it was terrible.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I-- that's when I lost my grandparents, in that winter, in-- in the winter of 1940-41.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And this went on for a few months until worse things came-- they happened-- started happening.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "We-- there were rumors going around that people are going to be deported.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And they-- they told us stories that, as there is not enough work in the ghetto, so these people are being deported to work on farms, in different places, in different-- In Germany, they needed people.",
      "word_count": 36
    }
  ],
